      "name": "Bench-top hemolysis loop validation — FDA pump geometry",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index against in vitro hemolysis loop measurements for five flow-speed operating points. RH predicted within 12% of measured values across all conditions; acceptance criterion RH < 1 satisfied.",
